Ignatius stayed low trying to avoid being hit. a blast hit near him
exploding sending the lone Trainer sliding across the sand. He rolled to his
feet fireing two missles at Shivah from the first and tird claw of his left
talon. His right talon fired 25 shots of energy at Kali .

Mech fluid was slowly seeping from his frame where a combination of weapons
had penetrated. He had to think of a way out. A sudden surge and a voice
came through his head. &quot;Head northeast, theres a sinkhole near the old
Predacon base. You can hide in there.&quot; Ignatius thought he was going insane
hearing voices. He decided to sort his sanity out later. Quickly the bot
leapt into the air transforming to his eagle form and flying in the
direction the voice had told him to go.
